SUMMARY

This directory contains data related to the 2018 Web Conference submission.  
A description of the study, which includes access to the paper, can be found at https://credibilitycoalition.org/research/.

This data has been anonymized to remove personal information related to the annotators, experts, and researchers involved in the study.   
In addition, internal platform links (URLs specific to the annotation platforms) have been removed.

ORIGINAL RELEASE DATE

2018-04-23

LICENSE

This dataset has been released under CC-0.  We appreciate attributions and would love to hear feedback at hello [at] credibilitycoalition [dot] org.


CONTENTS

* CredCoArticles-Snapshot-March 2018.anon.csv - list of articles used in the study (Boolean: "In WebConf") with expert scores (Decimal: "Expert score (1-5)") and annotator IDs

* Content Annotation Files - annotations associated with primarily content-related indicators
    * pe_schema_CredWeb3.txt - questions used in the study
    * pe_users_study-2018-03-19T18.anon.nolink.csv - results by question and annotator
    * pe-2018-01-35_articles-814_answers-2018-03-16T20.json - results for annotator PE-2018-01
    * pe-2018-02-32_articles-911_answers-2018-03-19T18.json - results for annotator PE-2018-02
    * pe-2018-03-39_articles-839_answers-2018-03-19T18.json - results for annotator PE-2018-03

* Context Annotation Files - per study, annotations associated with primarily context-related indicators
    * CheckAnnotationGuide_Anon.pdf - questions used in the study
    * credco-webconf-study-1_study-1-project-1_2018-02-21T22_43_18+00_00.anon.nolink.csv - results export 1
    * credco-webconf-study-2_study-2-project-1_2018-02-21T22_44_07+00_00.anon.nolink.csv - results export 2
    * credco-webconf-study-3_study-3-project-1_2018-02-21T22_44_40+00_00.anon.nolink.csv - results export 3
